value.0:
Place this invisible object in an area. Depending on the settings on this object traps will randomly be placed on any useable object or door in the area.

TRAP_PERCENTILE = 50%
This is the chance an object or door in this area will be trapped.

TRAP_TYPE = 2
This is the trap category.

An Invisible Trap Respawner(Random) must be placed in the area for these waypoints to work.

Place this waypoint in places where you want a possible ground trap to appear.

Note - No settings are needed for this waypoint the settings on the Invisible Trap Respawner(Random) are used.

For eg. If the Invisible Trap Respawner(Random) has a 33% chance of spawning traps in this area then each of these waypoints has a 33% chance of spawning a ground trap at their location.
